{"tid":1564693,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實今次唱國歌有莫大意義，絕不是雨傘嘉年華","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T07:00:55.000Z","uid":73783,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f2bd6eda761ae80c779399f63681b26721e0c14","tid":1564693,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:11:54.000Z","msg":"首先，在好多人心中<br />\n&lt;願&gt;已等同香港國歌<br />\n當咁多人在同時，同一個地方唱香港國歌<br />\n就加強了對香港這國家的認同感<br />\n雖然口中不說<br />\n但我相信在&lt;願榮光&gt;既影響下<br />\n認同港獨既人會增加<br />\n大大鼓舞了自己士氣<br />\n雖然最近暫緩了勇武的行動<br />\n但和理非既大合唱絕唔係嘉年華式<br />\n<br />\n而係好明顯顯示到<br />\n香港呢個民族已經出左黎<br />\n大家對香港足呢個身份認同<br />\n借音樂既感染下而團結起來<br />\n團結返香港人一定是重要的<br />\n無論之後勇武升級<br />\n又或者和理非行多步<br />\n都儲左一股莫大既能量<br />\n<br />\n所以今次大合唱絕有其重大意義<br />\n而非步上雨革後塵"},{"pid":"5122371d5547446ecf3c28518193be906609c200","tid":1564693,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:12:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c4ed5f073677e754e5d28a85ecdf16dae21fb118","tid":1564693,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27b3a2ae996755a76dd1271844c979a9a0f53183","tid":1564693,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2